					<msContents>
						<summary>

						<p>This inscription refers to the gift of 12 mā of land in Miḻalai nāḍu, a sub-division of Vaḍaveḷḷāṟṟūr nāḍu by the chief of Arantāṅgi for worshipping in the temple of Tiruvagattīśvaramuḍaiya-nāyaṉār. It is signed by Maṅgalarāyar of Māṅguḍi.</p>						

						</summary>
